      "Title": "Invex.Rez.Abstraction.FunctionCall",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Invex.Rez.Abstraction.FunctionCall.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Contains the arguments for a Rez function call.\n<br><br>\nWhen an <xref href=\"Invex.Rez.Abstraction.IResolver\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> encounters a function in a Rez template (e.g., <code>{name(args)}</code>),\nit constructs a <xref href=\"Invex.Rez.Abstraction.FunctionCall\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> from the text between the parentheses and passes it to the\nfunction delegate obtained from an <xref href=\"Invex.Rez.Abstraction.IResolverSource\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
