      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Invex.Rez.Configuration.ConfigResolverSource.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">An <xref href=\"Invex.Rez.Abstraction.IResolverSource\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> that resolves variables from an <xref href=\"Microsoft.Extensions.Configuration.IConfigurationRoot\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.<br>\nFunctions are not supported by this source.</p>\n"
