      "Title": "Invex.Rez.Configuration.IResolvableConfig",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Invex.Rez.Configuration.IResolvableConfig.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">An <xref href=\"Microsoft.Extensions.Configuration.IConfigurationRoot\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> whose values are resolved with an <xref href=\"Invex.Rez.Abstraction.IResolver\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> on read,\nallowing configuration values to contain Rez templates (e.g., <code>&quot;{baseUrl}/api&quot;</code>).</p>\n"
