      "Title": "Invex.Rez.Implementation.Resolver",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Invex.Rez.Implementation.Resolver.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">The default implementation of <xref href=\"Invex.Rez.Abstraction.IResolver\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.<br>\nResolves variables (e.g., <code>{name}</code>) and functions (e.g., <code>{name(args)}</code>) in a Rez template\nby querying registered <xref href=\"Invex.Rez.Abstraction.IResolverSource\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> instances in the order they were added.</p>\n"
